{"tid":2359920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"星二代爆遭性侵懷孕！哭找「孩子爸」隔1個月突有詭異舉動","createTime":"2021-01-09T09:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T11:12:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32c14abe7825bb4141e8d493a4e597a00761bef1","tid":2359920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"星二代坂口杏里外表清純，近年來卻不斷傳出負面消息，不但被爆出沉迷牛郎店，將已逝母親坂口良子的遺產敗光光，還下海拍AV、做外送茶等賣身還債，去年還自爆自己遭性侵懷孕，但不知道孩子父親是誰。沒想到近日又突然有詭異舉動，曬出自己的自拍照，說自己像女偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/24/2843527-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F24%2F2843527-PH.jpg&h=10f245c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲坂口杏里曾有明星夢。（圖／翻攝自坂口杏里IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/24/2843528-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F24%2F2843528-PH.jpg&h=830ab104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坂口杏里在自爆自己目前懷有身孕，是遭人性侵才懷上孩子的，且還不知道孩子的爸爸是誰，想等生完小孩再去驗DNA之後過幾天卻又繼續上班，引發懷疑。7日晚間曬出自己去染頭髮的照片，開心自拍說自己超級可愛，還問粉絲說自已「看起來像ＸＸ坂的女偶像嗎？」自信滿滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/09/2976805-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F09%2F2976805-PH.jpg&h=0c0a6fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲坂口杏里說自己像女偶像被吐槽。（圖／翻攝自坂口杏里IG）<br />\n<br />\n沒想到這句話慘遭網友吐槽，回是「暗黑坂嗎」、「像下滑的那種坂」讓她超尷尬。也因此再度登上日本媒體版面。據悉坂口杏里在媽媽去世3年，就把遺產全敗光在牛郎店上，為了維生，她不惜下海當AV女優，和男優上演激烈肉搏戰，可惜推出後惡評如潮，也讓她成為不少人茶餘飯後的話題。"},{"pid":"649633f95f25a63ee6265439be9c3bcaa929c645","tid":2359920,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"等我接手"},{"pid":"28e8b71558799bef83504d430789bbeb001ec299","tid":2359920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649633f95f25a63ee6265439be9c3bcaa929c645","tid":2359920,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"等我接手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"short左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707ffe913a77e36ecf21a50574ae764b535d64fe","tid":2359920,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"彩有無俾班老細性侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd61166eb6171c658756ed0e08ac90038eb4f8c","tid":2359920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707ffe913a77e36ecf21a50574ae764b535d64fe","tid":2359920,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"彩有無俾班老細性侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"100%無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bef7076dc3d6e0635deaa3a5b2113a25799039a","tid":2359920,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"番號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a27ce32c0e401e6c4068bdf660c382163e9de48","tid":2359920,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"好想屌呢啲白滑女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f540d99298a3cb4483c6935972f138a8d2514097","tid":2359920,"uid":302117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"TEK-085<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a0bca80d3f5b4be1d534c8c74936627df2c15e","tid":2359920,"uid":384534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a27ce32c0e401e6c4068bdf660c382163e9de48","tid":2359920,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"好想屌呢啲白滑女女<